<br>
First only those who are level 56 + for clerics and Level 55 + for enchanters and warriors would get to roll on the epics parts. The Rolls would be 200 - 500<br>
<br>
Any other loot that drops will be random to all who attened and can use the item<br>
<br>
Second only one epic piece, per guild, per class, per raid.<br>
<br>
Thirdly would like to keep to 6 groups all 50+<br>
<br>
Forthly (is something I am throwing out but really not sure it would go over well) any class who attended more raids than other would get a higher roll number save + 50 to every raid they attend.<br>
<br>
<br>
The raid would start at 12pm EST on a weekend run to 8 PM EST more than likely on a Sunday. That would be a chance of at least 4 Kings per raid and probably 2 enchanter maybe more depending on how fast we get this done not saying how many warrior cause it all depends on how the raid goes.<br>
<br>
A rogue will be needed for the raid also so unless we can get one to open the door this wouldn't happen. I would be willing to do this on a weekly sechdule as long as it went smoothly and quickly.<br>
<br>
Any suggestions are welcome.<br>
<br>
Thanks<br>
